                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5309" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0784</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9530 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“白马股”到“黑天鹅”——K公司的财务舞弊之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From White Horse Stock to Black Swan ——K the way of financial fraud</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">侯俊华，朱金等，刘敏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京康得新复合材料股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">K公司；财务舞弊；公司治理；舞弊三角理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">K company;financial fraud;corporate governance;fraud triangle theory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">K公司作为我国新型复合材料行业的领军者，一度被誉为“中国的3M”和“千亿白马股”。但2019年初，K公司被媒体爆出涉嫌财务舞弊行为，随即在资本市场引起轩然大波。经查发现，K公司在2015-2018年期间通过虚构、采购等方式虚增营业成本和研发收入，以此来虚增利润119亿元。该行为严重违反了信息披露的准则，给企业和股民造成不可估计的损失。本案例以K公司“财务舞弊”事件为主线，首先描述了其从巅峰跌落到谷底的全过程，其次根据财报信息及相关会计准则分析了其舞弊手段，最后对其舞弊造成的后果及影响进行概述。试图通过对本案例的分析，培养学员运用财务报表、识别财务信息的能力，由此引导学员对防范上市公司财务舞弊措施进行深度思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">K company, as the leader of the new composite material industry in China, was once known as &quot;China&#39;s 3 M&quot; and &quot;100 billion white horse stocks &quot;. But in early 2019, K company was revealed by the media suspected of financial fraud, immediately caused a uproar in the capital market. After investigation, K company in 2015-2018 through fiction, procurement and other ways to increase operating costs and R &amp; D revenue, so as to increase profits of 11.9 billion yuan. This behavior seriously violates the standard of information disclosure and causes incalculable losses to enterprises and shareholders. Based on the &quot;financial fraud&quot; incident of K company, this case first describes the whole process from the peak to the bottom, and then analyzes its fraud means according to the financial information and relevant accounting standards. Finally, the consequences and effects of fraud are summarized. Through the analysis of this case, we try to train the students&#39; ability to use financial statements and identify financial information, so as to guide the students to think deeply about the measures to prevent financial fraud in listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务舞弊</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
